name: Reflections of Iwanoff
summary: If you are a fan of modernist architecture, in particular post war brutalism then this is the app for you! Reflections of Iwanoff rebuilds a long lost post modern house designed by Iwan Iwanoff. Iwanoff was a Bulgarian avant garde architect who operated in Australia from the early 1950's to the late 1980's. In Reflections of Iwanoff you will be guided on a personal tour with award winning Australian architectural historian Stuart Harrison, on the tour you will learn about the principles of modernist...
